    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This technique consists of the user impaling the target on his sword and then throwing him. The user makes a single melee attack with critical range increased by 2. If the attack hits the user throws his opponent 5 ft. per point of strength bonus he has in any direction he desires, and the target must make a reflex save or be knocked prone.<br><br>Material Focus -The user's Wato, katana, double katana or hansori.</p>\n",
